description:
Mark gives background of Peter and his writing of Second Peter. Mark talks of the major themes of the letter: living a Godly life, prophecy of Scripture, false teachers, and the Day of the Lord. 

Scripture
2 Peter

Director: Phil Smith
Stars: Wilbur Penn
